title: Web Scraping with Beautiful Soup
description: Using HTML and the Beautiful Soup Python library for web scraping.

title: Intro to Making Apps With Swift
description: Using Swift to create iOS apps from scratch.

title: Intro to Unity
description: We'll learn the basics of the Unity game engine and build a simple 3D game by the end of the workshop!

title: Intro to Coding with Scratch
description: We'll learn the basics of programming, from simple commands like moving to a position, to loops, conditional statements, and variables all in Scratch, a block coding language

title: Intro to Bash
description: Learn the basics of using the command line interface through the OverTheWire wargames!

title: Compiling the Code
description: A computer archecture introduction. We will be learning how computer software works from binary to high-level languages

title: The Potential for AI in Finance
description: We will use AI to create an investment portfolio . Using AI we will ask those who choose to participate to choose an industry within the public market and then from there choose a stock. With the help of AI they will analyze the companies 10k report (their yearly report) and create a pitch deck to sell the stock to the rest of the club.

title: Machine Learning
description: We'll learn about machine learning and experiment with creating our own machine learning models!

title: Prompt Engineering: Incorporating ChatGPT into your programs
description: We'll learn how to design a website with dynamic features that are linked to OpenAI's chatgpt!
